			"width": 231.78955078125,
			"height": 165,
			"text": "Python · Flask\nPort :5010 ext → :5000 int\n\nScrapers: Steam · Epic · GOG · Xbox\n\nGET /api/v1/games/search?name=\nGET /api/v1/games/compare?name=\nGET /api/v1/games/trending/<store>\n\nPublishes → game_prices_queue",
