		{
			"type": "text",
			"id": "oe1xSFcj",
			"x": 15.857111684172793,
			"y": 645.8914077495222,
			"width": 496.69189453125,
			"height": 187.55,
			"text": "→  solid arrow     HTTP/REST  (sync request-response)\n- - dashed arrow   SSE / AMQP  (async / streaming)\n↔  bidirectional   read + write  (Redis TCP)\n\nARCHITECTURAL STYLES\n  Layered            Browser → Frontend → Gateway → Services\n  Client-Server      HTTP request-response pairs\n  API Gateway        Single entry point :8080 — routes, auth, rate limit\n  Pipe & Filter      Middleware: CORS → requireAuth → rateLimiter → handler\n  Publish-Subscribe  Scrapper publishes AMQP → RabbitMQ → Gateway consumes\n  Event-Driven       RabbitMQ msg → EventEmitter → SSE push to browser",
			"originalText": "→  solid arrow     HTTP/REST  (sync request-response)\n- - dashed arrow   SSE / AMQP  (async / streaming)\n↔  bidirectional   read + write  (Redis TCP)\n\nARCHITECTURAL STYLES\n  Layered            Browser → Frontend → Gateway → Services\n  Client-Server      HTTP request-response pairs\n  API Gateway        Single entry point :8080 — routes, auth, rate limit\n  Pipe & Filter      Middleware: CORS → requireAuth → rateLimiter → handler\n  Publish-Subscribe  Scrapper publishes AMQP → RabbitMQ → Gateway consumes\n  Event-Driven       RabbitMQ msg → EventEmitter → SSE push to browser",
			"fontSize": 11,
			"fontFamily": 3,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"strokeColor": "#374151",
			"backgroundColor": "transparent",
			"fillStyle": "solid",
			"strokeWidth": 1,
			"strokeStyle": "solid",
			"roughness": 0,
			"opacity": 100,
